Your daily dose of Disney cuteness! Add #DisneyBaby to your photos for a chance to be featured on our official accounts. 
🛍 Shop our Instagram feed:

node.text:
“You make my heart fuller than a hunny pot.” – Pooh 🍯💭

For your chance to be featured on our page, share a photo of your baby and favorite Pooh-ism, use the hashtag #🍯💭 ! Don't forget to tag @DisneyBaby! 

📸 @shannashipin
There’s a book for every occasion. 📚 What are you and your little one reading? ⬇

node.text:
It’s #NationalLemonJuiceDay! 🍋 Share a photo of your baby tasting a lemon and tag us @DisneyBaby for your chance to be featured. We can’t wait to see those puckered faces! 😆

Don’t forget to make big slices of lemon, so that baby doesn’t put the whole slice in their mouth, and make sure baby is already on solids before introducing lemon! 💛
